"books-docs/free-software-free-society-selected-essays-richard-m-stallman-3rd-"
"edition\"> GNU Press</a>."
msgstr ""
"2021'de bu kitap <a href=\"https://shop.fsf.org/books-docs/free-software-"
"free-society-selected-essays-richard-m-stallman-3rd-edition\">GNU Press</"
"a>'ten alınabilir."

